---
import Default from '../layouts/Default.astro';

const title = 'Contact | TARIDE Foundation';
const description = 'How to reach the foundation.';
---

<Default title={title} description={description} pageId="contact">
  <div class="container-reading">

    <span class="page-eyebrow">TARIDE Foundation</span>
    <h1 class="page-title">Contact</h1>
    <p class="page-lede">
      The foundation does not run an on-site contact form. Email is the canonical channel.
    </p>

    <h2>General</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:info@taride.org">info@taride.org</a> reaches the board. Response within five working days for substantive enquiries; faster for press.
    </p>

    <h2>Technical review</h2>
    <p>
      Reviewers in telecom, security, privacy, or digital-identity practice: see the <a href="/review/">review programme</a> for what is currently being sought.
    </p>

    <h2>Specification feedback</h2>
    <p>
      Open an issue or pull request against <a href="https://github.com/TARIDE-org/docs" rel="noopener" data-umami-event="outbound-click" data-umami-event-url="https://github.com/TARIDE-org/docs">TARIDE-org/docs</a>. Substantive review prefers GitHub; broader questions go to the email address above.
    </p>

  </div>
</Default>
